---
const SITE_NAME = "The-Circle";
const BRAND_TAGLINE = "The-Circle is the brand. Discord and Fantasy are the products.";
const DISCORD_INVITE = "https://discord.gg/9rPcHQZ7SH";
---

<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="utf-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1" />
    <title>{SITE_NAME}</title>
    <meta
      name="description"
      content="The-Circle is a laid-back brand built around two things: a drop-in Discord hangout and a fantasy football hub."
    />
  </head>

  <body>
    <header class="top">
      <div class="container nav">
        <a class="brand" href="/">
          <span class="mark" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="name">{SITE_NAME}</span>
        </a>

        <nav class="links">
          <a href="/discord">Discord</a>
          <a href="/league">League</a>
          <a href="/about">About</a>
          <a href="/rules">Rules</a>
          <a class="pill" href="/join">Join</a>
        </nav>

        <a class="pill mobileJoin" href="/join">Join</a>
      </div>
    </header>

    <main class="container">
      <section class="hero">
        <div class="badge">Brand-first • product-driven</div>
        <h1>{SITE_NAME}</h1>
        <p class="sub">
          {BRAND_TAGLINE} A place you can drop into when you’re bored — hang out, game, watch stuff, or just talk.
        </p>

        <div class="cta">
          <a class="btn primary" href="/discord">Explore Discord</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href="/fantasy">Explore Fantasy</a>
          <a class="btn ghost" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
        </div>

        <p class="fine">
          No clout. No pressure. No “be active every day” nonsense. Just a clean setup and a chill vibe.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>Choose your lane</h2>
        <p class="note">
          The-Circle is the umbrella. Pick what you’re here for — or use both.
        </p>

        <div class="grid">
          <article class="tile">
            <div class="tileTop">
              <span class="chip">Product</span>
              <h3>Discord Hangout</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              A well-built Discord that isn’t centered around a creator, product, or one game. Drop in for voice, games,
              music, and movie nights — or just background company.
            </p>

            <div class="tileCta">
              <a class="btn primary" href="/discord">See how it works</a>
              <a class="btn ghost" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join now</a>
            </div>
          </article>

          <article class="tile">
            <div class="tileTop">
              <span class="chip">Product</span>
              <h3>Fantasy Football</h3>
            </div>
            <p>
              A cleaner, more fun home base for leagues. Standings, rules, trash talk, and league tools — built around
              your people, not ads and clutter.
            </p>

            <div class="tileCta">
              <a class="btn primary" href="/fantasy">Fantasy hub</a>
              <a class="btn ghost" href="/join">Get updates</a>
            </div>
          </article>
        </div>
      </section>

      <section class="card">
        <h2>The vibe</h2>
        <div class="pills">
          <span class="pill2">Low pressure</span>
          <span class="pill2">No cliques</span>
          <span class="pill2">Organized</span>
          <span class="pill2">Good voice quality</span>
          <span class="pill2">Come & go anytime</span>
          <span class="pill2">Adult-friendly energy</span>
        </div>
        <p class="note">
          Most “friends servers” are messy and fall apart. Most big servers are noisy and impersonal. The-Circle is meant
          to be a reliable middle ground: small enough to feel human, set up well enough to actually use.
        </p>
      </section>

      <section class="card final">
        <h2>Ready?</h2>
        <p>
          If you’re already on Discord a lot and want a reliable place to hang out, start here. You can lurk first —
          nobody’s going to hassle you.
        </p>
        <div class="cta">
          <a class="btn primary big" href="/join">Join The-Circle</a>
          <a class="btn ghost big" href={DISCORD_INVITE} target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">Join Discord</a>
        </div>
      </section>
    </main>

    <footer class="footer">
      <div class="container foot">
        <span>© {new Date().getFullYear()} {SITE_NAME}</span>
        <span class="muted">Brand • Community • Products</span>
      </div>
    </footer>

